Thirst;;75;;80;;R;;Sang-hyun (Song Kang-ho), a respected priest, volunteers for an experimental procedure that may lead to a cure for a deadly virus. He gets infected and dies, but a blood transfusion of unknown origin brings him back to life as a vampire. Now, Sang-hyun is torn between faith and bloodlust, and has a newfound desire for Tae-ju (Kim Ok-bin), the wife of his childhood friend.;;Mystery & thriller,Horror;;Park Chan-wook;;2009;;Song Kang-ho,Kim Ok-bin,Shin Ha-kyun,Kim Hae-sook,Oh Dal-su,Mercedes Cabral;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011304-thirst